;The quality of the map is relatively poor so the related PDB entry 6YS5 (A. baumannii ribosome-amikacin complex - 30S subunit head) was rigid body fitted into the map using Chimera X-0.9, tigecycline was placed into the density at the primary site, and one round of global real space refinement and local refinement were carried out using PHENIX and Coot respectively, using ligand restraints in both cases.
